<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/"><channel><title>Home on Pro Residential Services</title><link>https://proresidential.biz/</link><description>Recent content in Home on Pro Residential Services</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.147.0</generator><language>en-us</language><copyright>Pro Residential Services</copyright><atom:link href="https://proresidential.biz/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>About</title><link>https://proresidential.biz/about/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://proresidential.biz/about/</guid><description>Learn about Pro Residential Services and owner Phil DiRuzza, Licensed General Contractor.</description><content type="text/html" mode="escaped"><![CDATA[<h2 id="pro-residential-services">Pro Residential Services<a href="#pro-residential-services" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <path d="M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3"></path>
      <line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line>
   </svg></a></h2>
<p>Pro Residential Services is a full-service construction and remodeling company based in Middleboro, Massachusetts. We serve residential homeowners throughout Bristol, Plymouth, and Barnstable counties with honest assessments, quality craftsmanship, and fair pricing.</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="phil-diruzza--owner--licensed-general-contractor">Phil DiRuzza — Owner &amp; Licensed General Contractor<a href="#phil-diruzza--owner--licensed-general-contractor" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <path d="M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3"></path>
      <line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line>
   </svg></a></h3>
<p>Phil DiRuzza founded Pro Residential Services with a straightforward commitment: do quality work, treat people fairly, and stand behind every project. With over <strong>30 years of hands-on construction experience</strong>, Phil brings deep expertise to every job — whether it&rsquo;s a window replacement, a finished basement, or a full addition.</p>
<p>Phil holds a Massachusetts General Contractor license and personally oversees every project from estimate to completion. When a project calls for specialty trades, Phil works with a trusted network of licensed subcontractors who meet the same standard of quality.</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="contact-us">Contact Us<a href="#contact-us" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <path d="M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3"></path>
      <line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line>
   </svg></a></h3>
<p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:5089222353">(508) 922-2353</a><br>
<strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:proresidentialservices@gmail.com">proresidentialservices@gmail.com</a><br>
<strong>Location:</strong> Middleboro, MA</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="service-area">Service Area<a href="#service-area" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <path d="M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3"></path>
      <line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line>
   </svg></a></h3>
<p>We serve residential homeowners across the greater Middleboro–Lakeville area and beyond:</p>
<ul>
<li>Taunton · Bridgewater · Pembroke · Halifax</li>
<li>Plympton · Carver · Wareham · Plymouth</li>
<li>Throughout Bristol, Plymouth, and Barnstable counties</li>
</ul>
<p><em>Not sure if we cover your area? Give us a call — we are happy to help.</em></p>
<hr>
<h3 id="licensed--insured">Licensed &amp; Insured<a href="#licensed--insured" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <path d="M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3"></path>
      <line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line>
   </svg></a></h3>
<p>All work is performed under Phil&rsquo;s Massachusetts General Contractor license. We carry full liability insurance for your protection and peace of mind.</p>
